PrecisEnactment of the CCFTA REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of customs duties paid or payable on goods that were eligible for the CHILE TARIFF prior to January 1, 2002, but are no longer eligible as a result of amendments to the Harmonized Commodity Description and Coding System.
